[Name] Thunar-Archive-Plugin
[Summary] The Thunar Archive Plugin allows you to create and extract archive files using the file context menus in the Thunar file manager.
[Description] The Thunar Archive Plugin allows you to create and extract archive files using the file context menus in the Thunar file manager. For example, to create a new archive, 
just right click on the files and folders you want to add to the archive, right click on one of the selected files and select Create Archive... from the context menu.
[License] GPL
[Homepage] http://www.foo-projects.org/~benny/projects/thunar-archive-plugin/
